## Precedence Order

When MDCs conflict:

1. **NeverSmall OS** (`neversmall-os.mdc`) – Highest precedence
2. **Agent Guardrails** (`neversmall-agent-guardrails.mdc`) – Safety rules
3. **Narrative Standards** (`neversmall-narrative-standards.mdc`) – Content rules
4. **Brand Standards** (`neversmall-brand-standards.mdc`) – Visual rules

