## MDC vs Intelliprop MDCs

This workspace contains two sets of MDC files:

### NeverSmall MDCs (`.cursor/rules/`)
- `neversmall-os.mdc` - Core operating system
- `neversmall-agent-guardrails.mdc` - Agent behavior rules
- `neversmall-narrative-standards.mdc` - Voice and tone
- `neversmall-brand-standards.mdc` - Visual identity
- `neversmall-mdc-index.mdc` - This index

**Purpose:** Rules for NeverSmall brand, website, and content work.

### Intelliprop MDCs (workspace root)
- `intellipropos.md` - Intelliprop Dev OS
- `intelliprop-*.md` - Various Intelliprop-specific rules

**Purpose:** Reference material from Intelliprop project (separate business).

**Note:** When working on NeverSmall website/content, use NeverSmall MDCs. Intelliprop MDCs are reference material only.

